BE ASSERTIVE, BUT
NOT TOO AGRESSIUE.
BE ARTICULATE,BUT
NOT PROFESSORIAL.

SOFT. WORK IN

BORING THEM WITH
THE DETAILS,
DONT SAY
ANYTHING
STUPID.
